# ðŸ’Œ Letter to My Favorite Person

An interactive project in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create personalized digital letters for special people.  
**Note:** The system interface is in Brazilian Portuguese (pt-BR).

---

## ðŸŒŸ Features

- Customize the **recipient's name**, **letter title**, and **message**.
- Preview your letter before sharing.
- Share your letter via **copied link**.
- Visual effects:
  - Heart animations following the mouse
  - Confetti when opening the letter
  - Animated seal
- Automatic draft saving using **localStorage**.
- Responsive design and print-friendly.

---

## ðŸ›  Technologies

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Gradients, variables, animations)
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Canvas for visual effects

---

## ðŸ“„ How to Use

1. Open `index.html` in your browser.
2. Fill in the **Name**, **Title**, and **Message** fields.
3. Click **"Aplicar na carta"** (Apply to letter) or **"PrÃ©-visualizar"** (Preview) to see your letter.
4. Click **"Compartilhar"** (Share) to copy a personalized link.
5. Double-click the ðŸ’– seal to add your signature.

---

## ðŸŽ¨ Customization

- Colors and styles are defined via **CSS variables**.
- You can easily change background colors, letter design, text colors, and visual effects.

